orth|last=Western|first=Dan|date=2018-09-06|website=Wealthy Gorilla|language=en-US|access-date=2019-12-21}}</ref>\n|[[Jay-Z|Shawn Carter]], [[Beyonc\u00e9|Beyonc\u00e9 Knowles-Carter]]\n| 1.5 (2019)\n|[[Hip hop music|Hip-hop]]/[[Rhythm and blues|R&B]], [[Roc Nation]], entrepreneurship\n| United States\n|-\n| West <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.foxbusiness.com/business-leaders/kanye-west-debt-yeezy-empire|title=Kanye West praised for turning $53M in debt into $1B Yeezy empire|last=Lam|first=Katherine|date=2019-07-11|website=FOXBusiness|language=en-US|access-date=2020-01-22}}</ref>\n|[[Kanye West]], [[Kim Kardashian|Kimberly Kardashian-West]]\n| 1.5 (2020)\n|[[Hip hop music|Hip-hop]]/[[Rhythm and blues|R&B]], [[Adidas Yeezy|Yeezy]], fashion, entrepreneurship\n| United States \n|-\n| Sarkisov<ref name=\"CrimeRussiaList\"/>\n| \n| 1.4 (2016)\n| [[RESO-Guarantiya]] Insurance company\n| Russia\n|-\n| Sharbately<ref name=\"forbesmiddleeast2017\"/>\n|\n| 1.3 (2017)\n| Investments, real estate, inheritance \n| Saudi Arabia\n|-\n| Bazhayev<ref name=\"CrimeRussiaList\"/>\n| \n| 1.25 (2016)\n| Alliance Group<!-- do not wikilink the New Zealand company -->\n| Russia\n|-\n| Greiner<ref name=austria's-richest/>\n| Hans Peter Haselsteiner\n| 1.23 (euros, 2014)\n| [[Greiner Group]], synthetic materials\n| Austria \n|-\n| Talbot<ref name=Financial-Review-Rich-List-Australia/>\n|\n| 1.21 (2013)\n| Resources \n| Australia\n|-\n| Haselsteiner<ref name=austria's-richest/>\n| Hans Peter Haselsteiner\n| 1.2 (euros, 2014)\n| [[Strabag AG]]\n| Austria \n|-\n| Rauch<ref name=austria's-richest/>\n| \n| 1.2 (euros, 2014)\n| Happy Day juices [[Rauch (company)|Rauch company]]\n| Austria \n|-\n| Rakhimkulovs<ref name=\"CrimeRussiaList\"/>\n| \n| 1.2 (2016)\n| [[OTP Bank]], oil company [[MOL Group]], [[Gazprom]] and [[VTB]]\n| Russia\n|-\n| Salteri<ref name=Financial-Review-Rich-List-Australia/>\n|\n| 1.17 (2013)\n| Manufacturing \n| Australia\n|-\n| Rossy<ref name=\"Canadian-Business-Richest\" />