013]]}} || ''Flight 404'' || [[Ditmar Award]] || Best Novella or Novelette || \n|-\n| align=\"center\" |{{sort|20132|[[2013 in literature|2013]]}} || ''Light Touch Paper, Stand Clear'' || [[Ditmar Award]] || Best Collected Work || \n|-\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n| align=\"center\" |{{sort|20133|[[2013 in literature|2013]]}} || ''Flight 404'' || [[Sir Julius Vogel Award]] || Best Novella or Novelette || <ref name=\"SJVW 2013\">{{citation | title = Sir Julius Vogel Award Results - 2013 |url=http://www.sffanz.org.nz/sjv/sjvResults-2013.html| publisher = SFFANZ | date = | accessdate = 2017-06-21}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"center\" |{{sort|20134|[[2013 in literature|2013]]}} || ''The Hunt For Red Leicester'' || [[Sir Julius Vogel Award]] || Best Novella or Novelette || <ref name=\"SJV 2013\">{{citation | title = Sir Julius Vogel Award Nominations - 2013 |url=http://www.sffanz.org.nz/sjv/sjvNominations-2013.html| publisher = SFFANZ | date = | accessdate = 2017-06-21}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"center\" |{{sort|20141|[[2014 in literature|2014]]}} || ''Difficult Second Album'' || [[Aurealis Award]] || Best Collection || \n|-\n| align=\"center\" |{{sort|20161|[[2016 in literature|2016]]}} || \"All the Colours of the Tomato\" || [[Aurealis Award]] || Best Science Fiction Novella || \n|-\n| align=\"center\" |{{sort|20171|[[2017 in literature|2017]]}} || \"All the Colours of the Tomato\" || [[Ditmar Award]] || Best Novella or Novelette || <\n|-\n| align=\"center\" |{{sort|20172|[[2017 in literature|2017]]}} || ''Matters Arising from the Identification of the Body'' || [[Aurealis Award]] || Best Science Fiction Novella || \n|-\n| align=\"center\" |{{sort|20181|[[2018 in literature|2018]]}} || ''Matters Arising from the Identification of the Body'' || [[Ditmar Award]] || Best Novella or Novelette || \n|-\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n| align=\"center\" |{{sort|20182|[[2018 in literature|2018]]}} || ''Matters Arising from the Identification of the Body'' || [[Sir Julius Vogel 